\id INT - SANGU Bible Translation
\rem Front matter for Genesis
\imt1 Ulutango ulwa kiyimba gina gayandiikhwe mu litaafili ili
\ip Pawutasi aMayandikhwa aManofu aga Lufingo uLukuulu gayandiikhwe kwa Shihebulaniya. Kihuma pina gayandiikhwe, gaganwilwe mu fimyanja finshi. Ilitaafili ili liganwilwe kihuma mu shilogolo sha Shihebulaniya. Baheene khanji lyaganulwagwa mu shimyanja sha Shingelesa ni Shiswahili. Panu wuyandiikhwe uwulongosi uwa kimutanga yuna iyimba ilitaafili ili, kiiva mu litaafili ili gakwali amaswi amahensa mu Shisangu.
\is1 1. Uwuganulaaji wa Maswi aMahensa ni Futinoti
\ip Mu Mayandikhwa aManofu gakwali amaswi aganji gina mahensa mu shimyanja sha Shisangu. Amaswi aga aganji gakwali kuwutasi wa litaafili ili, uluvala ulwa wuganulaaji wa Maswi aMahensa, gayandiikhwe shila liswi limo lina luganulo lwakwe.
\ip Aganji uluganulo ulunji luli pansi pawudugo wa wukulaasa (futinoti). Ifutinoti isinji siwonensa uluvala luna ukwiliile kipata pina gayandiikhwe mu mataafili aganji (Shiyanso 13:10).
\is1 2. Amataawa ga Nguluvi
\ip Mu litaafili ili nu Lufingo uLukuulu loona, uNguluvi imanyikha mandu kwa mataawa gavili.
\ip \pn Elohim\pn* – Ilitaawa ili likhangasa ishewo sha Nguluvi isha kiiva mutwa wa nyi. Mu litaafili ili, tiganwile ilitaawa ilyo \k Nguluvi\k*.
\ip \pn Yaahwe\pn* – Yaahwe litaawa lyakwe khamili. Uluganulo lwakwe \k One Nikwali yuna Nikwali \k*. Ndeeno, uNguluvi asikhawumbiilwe. Uluhaavi lumonga ilitaawa ili lipuliisikha Yehova. Mu litaafili ili, tiganwile ilitaawa ilyo \k MUTWA\k*.
\is1 3. Ifipuga mu mayandikhwa ga litaafili ili
\ip Mu mayandikhwa ago gavishiilwe fipuga fipuga, kwa kiiva ya mola iya shipuga isho. Ifipuga ifi fisivishiilwe mu mayandikhwa ga pawukuulu aga Shihebulaniya. Uwuganulaaji uwunji wa Mayandikhwa aManofu aga luhaavi ulu gana fipuga.
\ip Uluvala ulunji inkhalala sivili sivishiilwe panu pamo, baheene ishilogolo shikhale wunofu shina shishwali iShisangu (Shiyanso 12:4-5).
